description:
This is a 16 minute workout called '15 Minute Beginner Workout: Treadmill Virtual Scenery (Slow Jog/Fast Walk)' from the channel Turi's Adventures.
The workout falls under Cardio/Treadmill and Cardio/Walking.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Treadmill for this workout.
The workout has a The Mindful Walk and The Nature Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: 15 Minutes of Virtual Scenery for your Treadmill. The pace is a slow jog or fast walk. Good for beginners:)

The setting is a beautiful bridge over water.

Check out my other walking videos here: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLs2S4w7G9RePBYggRtkcnhRtfMDYobqFZ...
